<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, April 13 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
dropped six HK dollars to close at 2,611 HK dollars a tael on
Tuesday, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers
in Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 282.85 dollars a troy ounce, or
down 0.65 U.S. dollars from the previous close at Tuesday's
exchange rate of one U.S. dollar against 7.7485 HK dollars.
