<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, April 13 (Xinhua) -- Manila Police said Tuesday that a
carpenter was shot dead by an unidentified gunman for refusing to
pay his past gambling debts Monday night in Muntinlupa City of
Metro Manila.
</P>
<P>
The killed was Nolando Pasion, 40, a gambler and of Joaquin
Compound, Barangay Alabang, Muntinlupa City.
</P>
<P>
