stomach and died on the spot.
</P>
<P>
The suspect swiftly fled after the shooting incident, police
said.
</P>
<P>
Pasion was allegedly walking towards a store at about 11:30
p.m. local time Monday, when the suspect, armed with a firearm of
undetermined caliber, fired twice at him.
</P>
<P>
Prior to the shooting, the suspect suddenly appeared from
nowhere and forcibly demanded that the victim pay his debts.
</P>
<P>
But the victim refused, causing the suspect to shoot him.
</P>
