<P>
Philippines' New Interior Secretary Sets Priorities
</P>
<P>
MANILA, April 13 (Xinhua) -- Philippines' Newly-appointed Secretary
Ronaldo Puno, of the Department of Interior and Local Government
(DILG) set his top priorities as reform and modernization programs at
the Philippine National Police (PNP), fire and jail services.
</P>
