programs that will ensure the effective implementation of food
security, devolution and the fight against illegal drugs," Puno said.
</P>
<P>
Also included in his priorities are the expansion of the Street
Watch 117 program nationwide, continuation and creation of new
foreign-assisted program areas, and strengthening and rationalizing
local government corporate power on financing or projects.
</P>
<P>
Puno also vowed to strengthen the training program for officials
and personnel of the PNP, fire and jail bureaus and housing program
for members of the uniformed sector. 
