<HEADLINE> China Criticizes India for Missile Test </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 13 (Xinhua)-- China today criticized India for
testing a medium-range ballistic missile, saying that it is a
violation of UN resolutions that may spark a new arms race in
south Asia.
</P>
<P>
