<HEADLINE> 1999 Playoff Summary </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, April 11 (Xinhua) -- Following is the NBA 1999
playoff summary through games of April 11:
</P>
<P>
EASTERN CONFERENCE:
</P>
<P>
Team  (W-L)  Games Remaining (Home/Away) Games Back
